tasks.description:
Create `apps/admin/src/components/entity-list/filters/__tests__/filter-utils.test.ts` with tests from spec section 13.1:

extractActiveFilters tests:
- No URL params + no defaults -> {}
- No URL params + config defaults -> { destinationType: 'CITY' }
- URL param overriding default -> { destinationType: 'TOWN' }
- Sentinel clears default -> {}
- Ignores params not in config
- Handles multiple filters

computeDefaultFilters tests:
- undefined config -> {}
- Extracts only filters with defaultValue

filtersEqual tests:
- Identical objects -> true
- Different values -> false
- Different keys -> false
- Both empty -> true

buildFilterChips tests:
- Marks default-origin chips (isDefault: true)
- Marks user-applied chips (isDefault: false)
- Sorts by order
- Skips unknown filters

buildFilterParamUpdate tests:
- Sets value: { status: 'ACTIVE' }
- Clears with sentinel when hasDefault: { destinationType: '__cleared__' }
- Removes when no default: { status: undefined }

Target: 100% line coverage on filter-utils.ts
